attributes.title: Trump
attributes.review:
As soon as I downloaded and opened this app, I was greeted with a huge orange cheeto puff! It scared the living soul out of me. I went to Google to see if I could press charges for the jump scare, only to find the multiple instances of racism, bigotry, xenophobia, and pedophilia associated with Mr. Cheeto! What an awful puff running this country. 

Arrest the cops who murdered Breonna Taylor. Defund the police. Abolish ICE. Vote in November.
